<br />

<br />
The old easy way top slit mobs is up in smoke til lv70 mez. 200 range.
<br />

<br />
As above all things that made our job a wee bit easier, are gone with the new songs.  100 range mez is good only really for cc in camp.  Monks may even outpull us now in 50% of the situations.  Nice break from the pulling anyway.
<br />

<br />
Get to 70 and get that charm song...it is going to rock.  There will be ways to make that puppy work.  Pre nerf.
<br />

