				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Swarm Kiting with Charm (NOT PBAE Songs)<a name="63785"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Sep 23 04 10:29 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Who picked the names for various bard kiting.  For about 2 years I've known swarm kiting is basically reverse charm kiting social mobs.  Also have known that AE kiting is using PBAEs.  But I've even seen experienced bards mix up the terms (maybe those who group all the time).
<br />

<br />
I think everyone just thinks naturally that since there is a swarm of mobs when AEing it must be swarm kiting.
<br />

