				<td colspan="2"><span>Hey donvanlot...
<br />

<br />
Honestly, I don't understand why some people want to call AE swarming... I think the term swarm is perfectly apt for actual..reverse charmkiting...swarming.  What is a &quot;swarm&quot;..lets take bees for example...a bunch of creatures that gang up on enemies to defend one another.
<br />

<br />
That describes swarm kiting... to swarm they MUST be social-aggro.  
<br />

<br />
With AE, social don't matter.  Each one is attacking because you have attacked THAT individual.  The creatures in an AE kite can be ENEMIES.. it doesnt matter.. they individually wanna kill YOU because of the bastard YOU are.  That is an angry mob, not a swarm</span></td>
